What is Product Design? If you have little or no idea about this, you may want to visit our exhibition!

Desain Produk Universitas Pelita Harapan proudly presents Product Design Fair 2017: EUREKA!

This year's theme is Material Exploration. From wood to rattan, we use different types of materials to make a variety of products.

Do you want to know how to turn acrylics into beautiful pieces of jewelry or how to turn wood into lamps? Visit our exhibition at Plaza Indonesia on 27th - 30th July 2017 and find the answers!

L Y T U S - a little reminder to be humble in your desk

Inspired by lotus's life cycle both movement and its meaning in Buddhism.

L Y T U S is a desk lamp that remind you to be humble especially in your studies. Don't be arrogant when you in the up because you don't know when is your next down. So it's better to keep humble!

L Y T U S - a desk lamp inspired by Lotus

Lotus grow from muddy water to the surface and bloom beautifully, after bloom, lotus will wilt and return to the muddy water. In Buddihism, this phenomenon represent the up and down of a human life. 
L Y T U S is made from veneered plywood by laser cut and finished by wood filler, teak oil and semi doff top coat
